{"tid":1861801,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一天，一個中國人坐在醫院欣賞風景","createTime":"2020-02-04T09:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T10:09:02.000Z","uid":5343,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1301ae883b02af205dc16feb9d378f1781b26797","tid":1861801,"uid":5343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T09:49:32.000Z","msg":"一天,一個中國人坐在醫院欣賞風景,在醫院上,中國人問台灣人:「你有飛機大炮嗎?」<br />\n<br />\n台灣人說沒有,中國人就說:「那你的生命就要失去4分之1了。」過了一會兒中國人又問:「你有用支付寶嗎?」台灣人還是說不會用。中國人又說:「那你的生命又要失去4分之1了。又過了一會兒,中國人又問了:「你有5G嗎?」台灣人仍然說沒有,就在這時,狂風亂作,捲來一股病毒&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n台灣人問中國人:「你有口罩嗎?」中國人說沒有,台灣人說:「那你的生命就要玩完了!」<br />\n<br />\n中國人：&amp;$-/;%^]+#"},{"pid":"1561c2fdc2e02e90aa58da8ba5015e00ca5990f9","tid":1861801,"uid":303133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T09:52:30.000Z","msg":"玩完了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec9ee0b76d732f002f9c1bd321c2968c3c02b81","tid":1861801,"uid":5343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T09:54:08.000Z","msg":"有冇當年笑鳩台灣落後既巴打？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ea26adf00da9164792dfc4bf3e64e5a1ea4045","tid":1861801,"uid":2192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:09:02.000Z","msg":"香港人問澳門人<br />\n你有23 條嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}